org.infinispan.notifications.cachelistener.filter

Class DelegatingCacheEntryListenerInvocation<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.infinispan.notifications.cachelistener.filter.DelegatingCacheEntryListenerInvocation<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - cache key type
    V - cache value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CacheEntryListenerInvocation<K,V>, ListenerInvocation<Event<K,V>>

    public abstract class DelegatingCacheEntryListenerInvocation<K,V>
extends Object
implements CacheEntryListenerInvocation<K,V>
    A wrapper around a CacheEntryListenerInvocation that keeps a reference to the FilterIndexingServiceProvider instance that handles this invocation. All methods are delegated to the wrapped invocation except CacheEntryListenerInvocation.invoke(CacheEntryEvent, boolean) and ListenerInvocation.invoke(Object). FilterIndexingServiceProvider implementors must extends this class and implement its abstract unregister() method.
    Since:
    7.2
    Author:
    anistor@redhat.com
